subtitleNullable: An Anime Character Detection dataset in YOLOv8 format.
descriptionNullable: This dataset was originally collected as a part of the team project [AniRef-yolov8 ](https://github.com/SoulflareRC/AniRef-yolov8) at OPENMI at the University of Michigan.  This dataset contains over 7000 images from various anime for binary object detection tasks. The dataset is in YOLOv8 format.
